{"tid":2156943,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"只要足球上帝願意 他隨時能終結比賽","createTime":"2020-08-14T19:42:24.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-25T19:38:01.000Z","uid":54109,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"6e427d8d99c0e4bacff0b76e381dcb4d9e0bea1e","tid":2156943,"uid":54109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T19:42:24.000Z","msg":"賽後《每日體育報》給美斯打了10分的滿分，稱讚他是「國王」，評語表示：「美斯用了3分鐘就慶祝了第三個兒子的誕生，之後他攔截法比加斯，助攻迪比利攻入第二球。下半場攻入第三球。這場比賽是美斯+另外21人。上帝拯救國王。」<br />\n<br />\n世界體育報》則表示，巴塞依靠世界上最好的球員獲得了勝利，在球隊處於疑問中時，美斯帶領球隊前進。比賽開始後他迅速取得入球，打破平衡，之後又在一系列漂亮動作後助攻迪比利得分。在車路士夢想反勝的時候，美斯又用一個入球打擊了對手。這樣的表現只有最好的球員能做到。"},{"pid":"b6949fe625fd10af62f05c82bb4f0c9d62b05271","tid":2156943,"uid":54109,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T19:46:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hcj3mik.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fhcj3mik.jpg&h=73b63ef1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a881a1e4d90e381ec6a00436e86798be34cd7b2d","tid":2156943,"uid":53855,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T19:46:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f029ac32261e91eb5cc76f6ee4a96ab7e117dec1","tid":2156943,"uid":247905,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T19:46:52.000Z","msg":"無能力就咪X踢歐聯啦"},{"pid":"17d4c48306198b830fc1adaf3fe4fe9b561405e7","tid":2156943,"uid":25345,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T19:47:10.000Z","msg":"8月15,陰，心情欠佳<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d1de953cdae097c559a4e9393533fe41b16dbb3","tid":2156943,"uid":54109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T20:53:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a22c1a8875a4bf7a14974a4d91057416066d9bbb","